<div id="wb_element_instance72" class="wb_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#e3b709;">BUENOS AIRES 4 days, 3 nights</span></strong></h3>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">The program includes the following services:</span></strong></h2>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"> </h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">* At Buenos Aires: Lodging in the chosen hotel with breakfast.</span></strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">*Transfers to Airport / Hotel / Airport/</span></strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">* City Tour.</span></strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">* Full day "The Gaucho`s party".</span></strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">* Dinner "Tango show".</span></strong><br>
 </h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong><span style="color:#000000;">Day 1: BUENOS AIRES.</span></strong></h2>

<p> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">Welcome to the Tango's city, we were waiting for you! Once you arrive the International Airport of Ezeiza, you will be taken to the chosen hotel. The rest of the day is free to begin feeling the demurrage. At night, lodging.</span></strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">Day 2: BUENOS AIRES.</span></strong></h2>

<p> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">The day starts with a good breakfast. During the morning it will take place a City Tour around the City. The rest of the day will be free to have full contact with Buenos Aires. We suggest you that at night you have a dinner with a Tango's Show at Carlos Gardel Corner. At night, lodging at the hotel.</span></strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">Day 3: BUENOS AIRES. </span></strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">Breakfast. Full day excursion "Gaucho Party ", including lunch tipic "Asado Criollo", folk music, gaucho skills. In the evening, we return to the city. It' s time to enjoy Buenos Aires night life. Lodging.</span></strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#000000;">Day 4: BUENOS AIRES. Breakfast. According to your flight time, you can still wall around Buenos Aires. Transfer to the Airport.</span></strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>
